data.description: Excellent investment opportunity to own a multi-family property in Jersey City. Rent both units or occupy one yourself. Oversized lot with a total of 7 onsite parking spaces with an additional parking on street. Detached garage space with electricity to use for storage or side hobby. Full basement with additional bathroom, laundry hookup, and office space. Currently zoned as a two family, but with city approval could potentially upgrade to a 3 family. You won't want to miss this one! Schedule your showing today.Please wear a mask while viewing this property.
